title: Al-Hadab
text: Al-Hadab () is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in <a href="Saudi%20Arabia">Saudi Arabia</a> it is located at 20°46′45″<a href="north">N</a> 40°47′54″<a href="east">e</a> and is 2647<a href="meter">m</a> or 8684 <a href="imperial%20foot">feet</a> in height above <a href="sea%20level">sea level</a>.
